{"id":897,"parent_id":890,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":897,"title":"Hosea 7","subtitle":"","short_title":"Hosea","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 7"],[".studySummary",["i","Israel is reproved for her many sins—Ephraim is mixed among the people."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.1","order":"02.29.007.60315"},["b","1"],"When I would have healed Israel, then the iniquity of Ephraim was discovered, and the wickedness of Samaria: for they commit falsehood; and the thief cometh in,",["i","and"],"the troop of robbers spoileth without."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.2","order":"02.29.007.60316"},["b","2"],"And they consider not in their hearts",["i","that"],"I remember all their wickedness: now their own",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"doings"],"have beset them about; they are before my face."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.3","order":"02.29.007.60317"},["b","3"],"They make the king glad with their wickedness, and the princes with their lies."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.4","order":"02.29.007.60318"},["b","4"],"They",["i","are"],"all adulterers, as an oven heated by the baker,",["i","who"],"ceaseth from raising after he hath kneaded the dough, until it be leavened."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.5","order":"02.29.007.60319"},["b","5"],"In the day of our king the princes have made",["i","him"],"sick with bottles of wine; he stretched out his hand with scorners."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.6","order":"02.29.007.60320"},["b","6"],"For they have made ready their heart like an oven, whiles they lie in wait: their baker sleepeth all the night; in the morning it burneth as a flaming fire."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.7","order":"02.29.007.60321"},["b","7"],"They are all hot as an oven, and have devoured their judges; all their kings are fallen:",["i","there is"],"none among them that calleth unto me."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.8","order":"02.29.007.60322"},["b","8"],"Ephraim, he hath",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"mixed"],"himself among the people; Ephraim is a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"cake"],"not turned."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.9","order":"02.29.007.60323"},["b","9"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"Strangers"],"have devoured his strength, and he knoweth",["i","it"],"not: yea, gray hairs are here and there upon him, yet he knoweth not."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.10","order":"02.29.007.60324"},["b","10"],"And the pride of Israel testifieth to his face: and they do not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"return"],"to the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"their God, nor",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"seek"],"him for all this."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.11","order":"02.29.007.60325"},["b","11"],"¶Ephraim also is like a silly dove without heart: they call to Egypt, they go to Assyria."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.12","order":"02.29.007.60326"},["b","12"],"When they shall go, I will spread my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"net"],"upon them; I will bring them down as the fowls of the heaven; I will chastise them, as their congregation hath heard."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.13","order":"02.29.007.60327"},["b","13"],"Woe unto them! for they have fled from me:",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"destruction"],"unto them! because they have transgressed against me: though I",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"have"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"redeemed"],"them, yet they have spoken lies against me."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.14","order":"02.29.007.60328"},["b","14"],"And they have not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"cried"],"unto me with their heart, when they howled upon their beds: they assemble themselves for corn and wine,",["i","and"],"they rebel against me."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.15","order":"02.29.007.60329"},["b","15"],"Though I have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"bound"],["i","and"],"strengthened their arms, yet do they imagine mischief against me."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.16","order":"02.29.007.60330"},["b","16"],"They return,",["i","but"],"not to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"most"],"High: they are like a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"deceitful"],"bow: their princes shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_16c"},"fall"],"by the sword for the rage of their tongue: this",["i","shall be"],"their derision in the land of Egypt."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.2a","order":"02.29.007.60331"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/5.22"},"Prov. 5:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.8a","order":"02.29.007.60333"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/separation"},"TG Separation"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.8b","order":"02.29.007.60335"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/24.5"},"Lev. 24:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.9a","order":"02.29.007.60337"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/stranger"},"TG Stranger"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.10a","order":"02.29.007.60339"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/rebellion"},"TG Rebellion"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.10b","order":"02.29.007.60341"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/9.13"},"Isa. 9:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.12a","order":"02.29.007.60343"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/12.13"},"Ezek. 12:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/17.20"},"17:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.13a","order":"02.29.007.60345"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/17.43.42-43"},"1 Ne. 17:43 (42–43)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.13b","order":"02.29.007.60347"},["b","13b"],["span.small","OR"],"would have redeemed them."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.13c","order":"02.29.007.60349"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/micah/6.4"},"Micah 6:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.14a","order":"02.29.007.60351"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/2.13.11-13"},"Morm. 2:13 (11–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.15a","order":"02.29.007.60353"},["b","15a"],["span.small","HEB"],"trained."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.16a","order":"02.29.007.60355"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/11.7"},"Hosea 11:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.16b","order":"02.29.007.60357"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/78.57"},"Ps. 78:57"],"."],["div",{"id":"16c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/7.16c","order":"02.29.007.60359"},["b","16c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/17.5.1-6,24"},"2 Kgs. 17:5 (1–6, 24)"],"."]]}
